I"<h1 id="vscode-调试python代码时添加参数args"><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/zk0272/article/details/83105574">vscode 调试python代码时添加参数（args）</a></h1>

<ol>
  <li>打开<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Debug-&gt;Open Configurations</code>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tian-guo-guo/cdn@master/assets/picgoimg/20200713182958.png" alt="image-20200713182958776" /></li>
  <li>在对应的代码块中添加args，如下图（注意参数之间需要用字符串分割开，用空格是不行的）
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tian-guo-guo/cdn@master/assets/picgoimg/20200713183029.png" alt="image-20200713183029569" /></li>
  <li>再次运行，可以看到结果如下图，自定义的命令已经添加进去了
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tian-guo-guo/cdn@master/assets/picgoimg/20200713182916.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述" /></li>
</ol>
